<figureCitation id="13557D90BB125D2DD0F0069E4523FD7D" box="[159,260,729,755]" captionStart="FIGURES 3–4" captionStartId="4.[151,264,749,774]" captionTargetBox="[157,1429,187,722]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,181,724]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 3–4. Male terminalia of Hemerodromia deprimatura sp. nov. 3, lateral view of terminalia; 4, dorsal view of cerci. Abbreviations: cer=cerci, epa=epandrium, hyp=hypandrium, lsur =lower lobe of surstylus, usur=upper lobe of surstylus." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3734759" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3734759/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="552">Figs 3–4</figureCitation>
